public abstract class AbstractAttributeIndex<A,O>
extends Object
implements AttributeIndex<A,O>

A skeleton implementation of an index which implements the Index.supportsQuery(Query, QueryOptions) method, based on a set of queries supported by a subclass supplied to the constructor.

Author:
Niall Gallagher
